<html>
<head>
    <meta content="text/html;charset=utf-8" http-equiv="Content-Type">
    <meta content="utf-8" http-equiv="encoding">
    <title>New request to access your organisation</title>
    <style>
        li { margin: 1em 0;}
    </style>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0; color: #0b0c0c">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="15" cellspacing="0" border="0">
        <tr>
            <td width="100%" height="55px" bgcolor="#0b0c0c">
                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center">
                    <tr>
                        <td width="100%" bgcolor="#0b0c0c" valign="middle">
                            <img src=cid:logo alt="GOV.UK">
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <h1 class="email" style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 36px; line-height: 1.041666667; margin: 30px 0;">
        New request to access your organisation
    </h1>

    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>
        You have received this message because @Model.FullName has requested to gain access to @Model.OrganisationName via the Waste electrical and electronic equipment (WEEE) online service.
    </p>
    <p>To action this request <a href="@Model.ExternalUserLoginUrl">sign in to the WEEE online service</a></p>
    <p>This is an automated email; do not reply.</p>
    <p>If you have any enquiries, contact your environmental regulator:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><span>Environment Agency (England): 03708 506506</span></li>
        <li><span>Scottish Environment Protection Agency: 01786 457700</span></li>
        <li><span>Northern Ireland Environment Agency: 02 890 569338</span></li>
        <li><span>Natural Resources Wales: 0300 065 3000</span></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Regards,</p>
    <p>WEEE Team</p>
</body>
</html>